PROBLEM: I/P- N=1
         O/P- YES
         
         I/P- N=98
         O/P- NO
         
         Explain: 1 is equal to 2 raised to 0 (20 == 1).
         
         
         
SOLUTION:

bool isPowerofTwo(long long n)
{    
    for(int i=0;i<=(log2(n));i++)
    {
        if((pow(2,i))==n)
        {
            return true;
            break;
        }
    }
    return false;
}
